{"tid":590943,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"洪水橋191呎劏房賣372萬   呎價近兩萬媲美太古城","createTime":"2018-03-13T05:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T22:03:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2365846749936f6dd5976ac02f0be5e5ffb2510a","tid":590943,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:48:24.000Z","msg":"即時財經  2018-03-12 16:50:54 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n【新增影片】<br />\n<br />\n位置隔涉兼公屋式設計、由百利保（617）及同系富豪酒店（078）合作元朗洪水橋新盤尚築，每層劏超過30伙，整幢物業134伙中，99%單位面積不足300方呎，以開放式設計。發展商於2015年5月公佈首張價單，首批60伙折實平均呎價近1.18萬元，呎價貴絕鄰近住宅物業三成，當時已被炮轟貴到離譜。<br />\n<br />\n但更離譜的是，未夠3年後的今日，當日的「離譜價」已變低價，因為這個位置吊腳到暈的洪水橋盤，業主轉個手又賺幾十萬，呎價更升至近2萬元，拍住港島太古城。<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，尚築地下15號特色戶，實用面積191方呎，另設71方呎花園，上月登記以372.8萬元易手，呎價19,518元除貴絕洪水橋外，亦料創下元朗歷來最貴二手呎價紀錄。原業主姓葉，2015年6月以一手價289.92萬元買入，當時呎價已達15,179元，短短兩年多升值82.88萬元，升值28%。由於持貨未夠三年，即使扣除10%SSD，賬面仍賺45.6萬元。<br />\n<br />\n區內代理透露，上址今年1月已放盤，叫價400萬元。屋苑現有約5個二手放盤，叫價380萬至400萬元。"},{"pid":"99e65935c42da8ecc37b4eb032e9795d5b9f4e8d","tid":590943,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d04b8dc02d32b5ccb71ace2c039d152b29e1853","tid":590943,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T06:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3027b99b2e23a2a12e0b78eb6dcb6051f94f79e8","tid":590943,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73861c8c9153a5020df1122172f9bcdc2d3c12fa","tid":590943,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a3b9689ecb0d11f5f9abe9293d87b47aef3e01","tid":590943,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T15:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750556ab165d5fe74c31cc31b8cc6a474c70497e","tid":590943,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T17:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce229de9d1f1c89113afb6cf4b8afc319ef27581","tid":590943,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T17:05:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4938e280a45194340d238d9b6bbf2b33965263c3","tid":590943,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T21:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c25c60b0ca5e2583e23f14562cafaa3a83ad84","tid":590943,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T22:03:52.000Z","msg":"我見屯門有人三百幾呎放租5000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}